originalText.text: I had such a bad experience with this apartment. I called multiple times to ask questions but the staff didn’t speak English to give me the informations needed. Had to text them the whole time and they told me to send my email so they could give me the informations about the hotel but ended up never doing it. Canceled my reservation last minute and said i never sent a confirmation form to them. Sadly I can’t give 0 stars because if I could I would
